body:
I'm guessing here, but i bet that your userCustomEPLibrary.idf or OpenStudioMasterTemplate.idf are faulty. Can you check them? I would move them to another location (not in the LB_HB path), close GH and Rhino and open them again. That should cause to download those files again.

Check also [this discussion](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topics/openstudiomastertemplate-idf-to-use-honeybee).

Maybe i'm wrong though ...

-A.
